==Equipment==
<tabber>
Magic =
Using magic alongside the [[dragon claws]] will allow the player to kill the Mimic relatively quickly. High-levelled players should have little difficulty defeating the mimic with high-end gear.
<br>
The player should always use [[Protect from Melee]] and move around the room when the Mimic throws sweets, and the player should ignore the spawned [[Third Age minions]]. Protect from Melee should be activated before the player enters the instance. The player should use stat-boosting potions and the ''invigorate'' option of the [[Imbued heart|imbued]]/[[saturated heart]] before entering the instance. The player should enter the fight in full melee gear and use both the dragon claws special attacks (can be substituted with [[burning claws]] or a [[dragon dagger]] if the player does not have dragon claws).
<br>
For lower-levelled players, it is helpful to freeze the Mimic in place with [[Entangle]] or [[ice spells]], which renders the Mimic unable to use melee attacks or the stomp attack as long as you are standing away from it.

